          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The experiment features were taken from the paper of",
                " REL-REF.",
                "The differential cross section of the",
                " 40Ca(gamma,p0)39K process has been measured in the",
                " energy range Egamma = 100 - 300 MeV at laboratory",
                " angles of 45, 90, and  135 degree. The cross section",
                " for the (gamma,p) reactions leaving 39K in its ground",
                " state was extracted from the tip region of the proton",
                " spectra measured at a series of bremsstrahlung",
                " end-point energies. The data were compared with a",
                " distorted-wave impulse-approximation calculation",
                " based on a direct,single-particle knockout mechanism."
              ]
            }
          ],
